{"tid":727610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"任志剛建議取消聯繫匯率制度 舌戰財政司金管局","createTime":"2018-07-03T07:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T07:21:36.000Z","uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f2206196c3071c6e6f79bea75f762ab07f616df3","tid":727610,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:05:25.000Z","msg":"前任香港金融管理局總裁任志剛發表《香港貨幣體制的未來》一文，指出香港匯率制度還可以轉為匯率走廊，與美元、人民幣或成分保密的一籃子外國貨幣掛鉤。<br />\n此言論掀起軒然大波。包括當時的財政司司長曾俊華、金管局現任總裁陳德霖、立法會議員，以及有香港&ldquo;聯繫匯率之父&rdquo;之稱的祈連活在內的相關方應聲予以駁斥。2012年06月12日"},{"pid":"0658a940653bb8c0934010e9728adfd6d111319f","tid":727610,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:07:02.000Z","msg":"【港股大跌過900點】<br />\n【人民幣貶值幅度加大】<br />\n<br />\n港股上午大跌，指數曾經跌超過 960 點。<br />\n<br />\n人民幣貶值幅度加大，加上內地 A 股周一重挫，恒指低開 338 點後，指數跌勢進一步擴大。<br />\n<br />\n曾經跌過 900 點，指數跌至 28,000 點邊沿，為去年十月以來最低水平。<br />\n<br />\n之後跌幅一度收窄，不過 11 點鐘過後，沽壓再度增大，指數一度跌穿 28,000 點，跌過 964 點，低位見過 27,990 點。"},{"pid":"3c546f0ff8c212b6a6b001d1eb3ec0d5f1bdd0df","tid":727610,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:19:38.000Z","msg":"Source or mother?"},{"pid":"70b3c2bc4517f25eddc7de056b9ca79f7e38b22e","tid":727610,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c546f0ff8c212b6a6b001d1eb3ec0d5f1bdd0df","tid":727610,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:19:38.000Z","msg":"Source or mother?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/152022_2818501c61bc922f9be37435b69535fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F152022_2818501c61bc922f9be37435b69535fb.jpg&h=224f16b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d4d200f016c6b4e4563fb4a15743713e76578fa","tid":727610,"uid":176111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:21:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2012年6月12日</span></span>"}]}